{"tid":2032801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[賣港賊] 香港國安法 副總理韓正接見政協解說；港區人大政協發聲明　支持立法","createTime":"2020-05-24T09:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T09:18:09.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc81a1fde0ff55c9d95e2686f84e36dbf41ae877","tid":2032801,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"在北京，國務院副總理、主管港澳事務的中共政治局常委韓正早上接見港澳政協委員，解說人大為香港國家安全立法的迫切性。有政協引述韓正指，香港有反對派以「攬炒」危害一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n港區全國人大代表及政協委員分別發表聲明，支持香港國家安全法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5p78ExzYpUg&amp;t=166s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5p78ExzYpUg%26t%3D166s&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=700deae8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5p78ExzYpUg&amp;t=166s</a>"},{"pid":"cf23ed1fb59fb198e6b11448aa9b305fc7a02125","tid":2032801,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"[推到所有人都嗌］香港獨立 唯一出路嘅英文口號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2032783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2032783</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}